      "audioFile": "drifter_match_start_drifter_bebop_convo01_02",
      "audioUrl": "audio/drifter_match_start_drifter_bebop_convo01_02.mp3",
      "text": "Been travelin' a long way to get here\u2026haven't had time to rest up and get a proper meal.",
      "duration": 6.706
    },
    {
      "order": 3,
      "character": "Bebop",
      "audioFile": "bebop_match_start_drifter_bebop_convo01_03",
      "audioUrl": "audio/bebop_match_start_drifter_bebop_convo01_03.mp3",
      "text": "In that case you should come over to the scrap yard after the ritual.  I'm sure Miss Shelly could help out with dinner.",
      "duration": 5.165
    },
    {
      "order": 4,
      "character": "Drifter",
      "audioFile": "drifter_match_start_drifter_bebop_convo01_04",
      "audioUrl": "audio/drifter_match_start_drifter_bebop_convo01_04.mp3",
      "text": "Thanks for giving me something to look forward to Bebop",
      "duration": 3.345
    },
    {
      "order": 5,
      "character": "Bebop",
      "audioFile": "bebop_match_start_drifter_bebop_convo01_05",
      "audioUrl": "audio/bebop_match_start_drifter_bebop_convo01_05.mp3",
      "text": "My pleasure.",
      "duration": 1.187
    }
